  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的数据流向图。最顶层是MQTT Broker，负责接收所有设备的消息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Broker放在顶部。那数据从Broker出去之后流向哪里？是直连云端还是先经过边缘节点处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "工业场景里通常先经过边缘节点做本地预处理，再上报。所以Broker下面应该连一个EdgeNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把这两个节点加上，用从上到下的流向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说的可能有点跳跃。实际上Broker和EdgeNode之间还有一个环节——边缘侧通常也有个本地Broker做协议转换，然后再到EdgeNode做计算。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，那我需要在中间插入一个节点。现在变成：云端MQTT Broker → 边缘MQTT Broker → EdgeNode，这样三层结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但注意这两个Broker虽然功能类似，但在工业架构里角色不同——一个是中心Broker，一个是边缘Broker。EdgeNode最终做数据过滤和本地决策。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。现在图上是三个节点垂直排列，两个Broker分别位于上中层，EdgeNode在底层，数据流向自上而下。",
      "elements_involved": [
